getRoleAdmin(bytes32).details: Returns the admin role that controls `role`. See {grantRole} and {revokeRole}. To change a role's admin, use {_setRoleAdmin}.

grantRole(bytes32,address).details: Grants `role` to `account`. If `account` had not been already granted `role`, emits a {RoleGranted} event. Requirements: - the caller must have ``role``'s admin role. May emit a {RoleGranted} event.

hedzClaims(address).details: Returns the number of HEDZ claims.

mintWithClaimsDiscount(uint256).details: Used to mint token(s) with claims discount.

mintWithOwnerDiscount(uint256,bytes32[]).details: Used to mint token(s) with owner discount.

mintWithPepeEditionsBurn(uint256,uint256.details: Used to mint token(s) with Pepe Editions burn.

mintWithZogzEditionsBurn(uint256,uint256.details: Used to mint token(s) with ZOGZ Editions burn.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pause().details: Used to pause sale. Emits {Paused} event(s).

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

renounceRole(bytes32,address).details: Revokes `role` from the calling account. Roles are often managed via {grantRole} and {revokeRole}: this function's purpose is to provide a mechanism for accounts to lose their privileges if they are compromised (such as when a trusted device is misplaced). If the calling account had been revoked `role`, emits a {RoleRevoked} event. Requirements: - the caller must be `account`. May emit a {RoleRevoked} event.

revokeRole(bytes32,address).details: Revokes `role` from `account`. If `account` had been granted `role`, emits a {RoleRevoked} event. Requirements: - the caller must have ``role``'s admin role. May emit a {RoleRevoked} event.

setDiscountedMintPrice(uint256).details: Used to set discounted mint price. Emits {DiscountedMintPriceUpdate} event.

setHedzOriginalsContract(address).details: Used to set HEDZ Originals contract. Emits {HedzOriginalsContractUpdate} event.

setMerkleRoot(bytes32).details: Used to set HEDZ Originals contract. Emits {HedzOriginalsContractUpdate} event.

setMintPrice(uint256).details: Used to set mint price. Emits {MintPriceUpdate} event(s).

setNFTContract(address).details: Used to set NFT contract. Emits {NFTContractUpdate} event.

setPepeEditionsContract(address).details: Used to set Pepe Editions contract. Emits {PepeEditionsContractUpdate} event.

setZogzEditionsContract(address).details: Used to set ZOGZ Editions contract. Emits {ZogzEditionsContractUpdate} event.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

unpause().details: Used to unpause sale. Emits {Unpaused} event(s).

withdraw(uint256).details: Used to withdraw funds from the contract.

withdrawAll().details: Used to withdraw all funds from the contract.
